column2: Immune to Blind • Plays Gong • Dazes

<c=@abilitytype>Legendary Dwarf.</c> Launch a chain at your target and at foes around your target. When the chain connects with a foe, it slows and taunts them. You take less damage from taunted foes.
<c=@flavor>A light for exploring dark, dangerous places.</c>
Double-click to apply to an accessory, amulet, or ring with an unused upgrade slot.
Double-click to unpack a full set of level 80 armor.
Grant fury, might, and swiftness to yourself and nearby allies.
A gift used to create legendary weapons.
